data.description:
What an Opportunity! Features a 3/bed 2/bath Mother-in-Law suite! 
Use as an Income Producing property! A Large Family Vacation Home! or even an Office! Nestled in the prime business district of Downtown Gulfport. 

Currently used as a duplex with tenant in place who would love to stay! Side A (pictured furnished) is 2-stories with open and spacious layout. Just over 2,000sqft of living space and offers a split-level floor plan with several rooms that can easily be converted into a 5bd/3ba unit.

Side B (pictured unfurnished; photos taken prior to tenant move-in) features 3bd/2ba. Currently rents for $1350/mo. 

This LARGE lovely gem offers endless possibilities and multi-use. 

Just a short walk to the sandy beaches, Jones Park, the Mississippi Aquarium, Restaurants and Entertainment, but NOT located in a flood zone!!!

Priced to sell! 
With just a few minor repairs and a little TLC, this property is Prime! 

Closing Cost Assistance and Interest Rate Buy-Down Available!

Schedule a Tour today! Appointments Required. Pre-Approval Letters/Proof of Funds Required. 

Please Do Not disturb occupants.  
Buyer/Buyer's Agent to verify all information.
